python utf8scan and utf8scan2 code repositories
'Hello, world!' in utf8scan:
/U8S----------\
|■  ■   ■■  ■ |
|■■■ ■■  ■■ ■■|
|  ■■ ■■■■■ ■■|
|  ■     ■■■ ■|
|■■■■ ■■■■■■■ |
| ■ ■■ ■■  ■■ |
| ■  ■    ■   |
\-------------/
'Hello, world!' in utf8scan2:
/U8S2---------\
|=o o=oo■o=o=■|
| ■o■■o=o  o■o|
|■■o■■■ =■o=o=|
|o = o        |
\-------------/
Both automatically measure themselves to keep as much of a box shape as possible.
